= Source Mage Installation =

We have several ways that allow you to install Source Mage on your computer:

* [[Install/ISO|from the ISO]] -- **outdated**
* [[Install/USB|from the USB flash drive]] -- **outdated**
* [[Install/Chroot|from the chroot image]]

**Note:** outdated guides will be updated on the next ISO release, current recommended method is to install from the chroot image.